{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/JoinUsOnDiscord.png?t=1736237975\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/1_Bridge.png?t=1736237975\" />Manage resources while surviving and outrunning the impending storm chasing after you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/1_Bridge.gif?t=1736237975\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/2_DefendGIF.gif?t=1736237975\" />Fight blizzards and fiery tornadoes. Can you find ways to neutralize them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/2_Storm.gif?t=1736237975\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/3_Combat.gif?t=1736237975\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/4_Recruit.png?t=1736237975\" />Settlers are the lifeblood of your bridge settlement, operating buildings to ensure resources flow. Keep them fed, happy, and healthy, and assign specialized roles like farmers, scientists, or engineers to boost key structures. The bridge is more than a crossing\u2014it\u2019s a thriving community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/4_Agriculture.gif?t=1736237975\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/5_ResearchUpgrades.png?t=1736237975\" />Losing and restarting is expected! Permanent upgrades means you get stronger and progress further every time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/5_ResearchTree.gif?t=1736237975\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/6_CollectPetsGIF.gif?t=1736237975\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether it's 5 unicorns or a variety of mammals, amass your favorite pets to join you, each giving unique buffs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/6_Pets.gif?t=1736237975\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/7_Explore.png?t=1736237975\" />Navigate different biomes to uncover clues to the storm\u2019s origins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/7_Biomes.gif?t=1736237975\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/9_CustomizeTraitsGIF.gif?t=1736237975\" />Earn cosmetics ranging from glowing hair to fancy accessories! As you progress, unlock traits that offer bonuses like extra starting resources or faster building production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/9_CustomizeTraits.gif?t=1736237975\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3366680/extras/8_DecorateIslandBeautifyBridge.png?t=1736237975\" />Between runs, take your time to build your own peaceful isl